In addition, the court applied Article 64 of the Criminal Code of the Russian Federation, according to which it is possible to impose a punishment below the lower limit.
As for the assistant of Mamayev Vasily Seroshtanov, the court did not establish the circumstances that would become the basis for changing the category of gravity of the committed and changing the sentence.
Anton Mamaev himself said that he was dissatisfied with the decision of the Moscow City Court.
I am disappointed with the court’s decision.
